metadata.name: Homesick
metadata.description:
I've looked for this feeling of wholeness in every corner of life. I've traveled through every state I could in search of where my soul felt at peace. I've poured open every part of myself to wring out the pain I've experienced from living in a broken home. 

Even if I'm yearning for a place that doesn't exist yet I will never stop searching for it because it keeps me going to know my soul will inevitiably find home.
